----------------------------------------------------

Tests the `array` token: numeric arrays, key-value arrays, boolean arrays, IP address
arrays, string arrays, arrays with escape sequences and variable interpolation inside
string items, multi-pair key-value arrays. Also tests array items with all data types:
internal IDs, IP prefixes, IPv6 addresses and prefixes, date-times, dates, times,
durations, and bare fallback items.
